  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为医院门诊系统建一个ER图。核心实体应该是患者、医生和预约，患者可以有多条预约记录，但每条预约只对应一个患者。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PATIENT",
        "APPOINTMENT",
        "DOCTOR"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白，PATIENT到APPOINTMENT是一对多的关系。那医生这边呢，也是类似的患者预约模式吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DOCTOR",
        "APPOINTMENT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，医生也是一对多参与预约。另外还需要护士协助，护士也可以参与多条预约记录。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NURSE",
        "APPOINTMENT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把这三个参与方和预约的关系画出来。接下来是处方部分吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PRESCRIPTION"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，医生开处方，患者接收处方，处方里包含具体药品。这里要注意，一种药品可以被多次开具，但每次处方只对应一种药品。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PRESCRIPTION",
        "MEDICATION",
        "DOCTOR",
        "PATIENT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：PRESCRIPTION是连接DOCTOR、PATIENT和MEDICATION的关联实体吗？还是独立的实体？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PRESCRIPTION"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是独立实体，它有自己的ID、 dosage用量和duration_days疗程天数。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PRESCRIPTION",
        "dosage",
        "duration_days"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "了解了。现在加上科室DEPARTMENT，医生和护士都应该隶属于某个科室。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DEPARTMENT",
        "DOCTOR",
        "NURSE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，科室还要管理诊室ROOM，每个科室有多个诊室，预约需要在具体诊室里进行。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DEPARTMENT",
        "ROOM",
        "APPOINTMENT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "ROOM到APPOINTMENT的关系是：一个诊室可以安排多场预约，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ROOM",
        "APPOINTMENT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，而且预约记录里要存room_id、patient_id、doctor_id和nurse_id这些外键。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APPOINTMENT",
        "room_id",
        "patient_id",
        "doctor_id",
        "nurse_id"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "结构差不多了。我来补全各实体的属性字段，患者需要保险状态is_insured，药品需要标记是否处方药requires_prescription。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PATIENT",
        "MEDICATION",
        "is_insured",
        "requires_prescription"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，DOCTOR和NURSE的department_id应该和DEPARTMENT关联，但ROOM里的department_id我刚才没说清楚——诊室也是属于科室的，这个关系要补上。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DOCTOR",
        "NURSE",
        "ROOM",
        "department_id",
        "DEPARTMENT"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，DEPARTMENT到ROOM也加上了一对多关系。还有需要调整的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DEPARTMENT",
        "ROOM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "APPOINTMENT的appointment_date是date类型，PRESCRIPTION的duration_days是int表示天数，这些类型没问题吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APPOINTMENT",
        "appointment_date",
        "PRESCRIPTION",
        "duration_days"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，date和int类型都已设置。所有实体的主键都是int类型的id，字符串字段用string，布尔字段用boolean。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "id",
        "string",
        "boolean",
        "date",
        "int"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美，这个ER图覆盖了患者预约、医生开药、护士协助、科室诊室管理的完整流程，可以定稿了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PATIENT",
